data.description: Quaint home located in the coveted Mac Groveland neighborhood. Features include hardwood floors, crown molding, an updated bath with tile surround bath including tiled walls. Don’t forget about the oasis that awaits you off the oversized deck; relaxing and unwinding is made easy in the spacious 22x14 backyard, ideal for outdoor gatherings and leisure activities. There are expansion opportunities with its generous lot size. This property opens doors to exciting possibilities. Imagine creating your dream DADU garage and loft, offering both functionality and style. Unlock the potential of the lower level and attic which provides ample space for your personalized touch. The home is within walking distance to a variety of grocery stores, restaurants and more. Embrace the beauty of the nearby river parkway, with picturesque views and serene walks, providing the perfect escape from the city’s hustle and bustle.
